
# Kubernetes

- Kubernetes is open source orchestration platform which is used to deploy and manage containerize applications
- Kubernetes is orchestration tool (Orchestration = Container management tool)


- Cluster is group of nodes
- Pod is smallest unit of kubernetes
- Cluster consist of Master and slave

- Number of containers increased or decreased are controlled by kubernetes as per required
- K
# Kubernetes Architecture

# Pod
  - Pod is smallest entity in kubernetes

# Kubelet
  - Kubelet is responsible for running the pod
